"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"On Monday, a copy of [Startup CXO](https://www.amazon.com/Startup-CXO-Companys-Functions-Techstars/dp/1119772575), my friend Matt Blumberg’s new book, arrived at the USV office. I picked it up to take a quick look and thought “this a heavy book!”\\n\\nSo I texted Matt, congratulated him on getting the book out, and then asked why it was so heavy. He replied “because it is 640 pages, there is a section on every C-level function in that book.”\\n\\nThat’s when I realized that Startup CXO is not really a book. It’s a “field manual” to scaling a leadership team and company. It is the kind of book you will keep by your desk and pull out from time to time to figure out how to approach an issue or to help one of your senior leaders figure out how to do that.\\n\\nAnd in that context, it’s a very valuable resource for CEOs and leadership teams as they scale a company and find new challenges around every corner.\\n\\nThe book is now out in Kindle and Hardcover. I recommend the [Hardcover](https://www.amazon.com/Startup-CXO-Companys-Functions-Techstars/dp/1119772575) so you can keep it handy and pull it out from time to time when you need a quick primer on something.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1623241063,\"title\":\"Startup CXO\",\"publication\":\"avc\"},\"digest\":\"sz-CEpvzIAVo4YG-FV0fvpPtMoNHZcxOzMuCU4R2QAI\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xB8332710AB60A1B2e8FE6D775d83524C9E0cE136\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"kJLn-lC67aIvmvgqR9Udc9CBZQUmLGFW9DBcu0alOhQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"2_kBWCc1TX2FuV8c0n-mCnDNjOYkxCF8CRO668ovICk\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"p0IT28FVdvMuBGvspOsn6breVhho_VbAaFvkkwjd2cIOI7N5gORBLg3ZF4BD31MIbNn5t_w--pjcCqUcrMo8pw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x5c524663f349af75bf9b608e8016f98d5c6409af3557a61916ea67bf27388009285d4bd59c7f5f675a906f78ba214885a8753a19e5332df7592d6c1e2f5f6ba31c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize the publication of articles on avc.mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"kJLn-lC67aIvmvgqR9Udc9CBZQUmLGFW9DBcu0alOhQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"2_kBWCc1TX2FuV8c0n-mCnDNjOYkxCF8CRO668ovICk\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"sz-CEpvzIAVo4YG-FV0fvpPtMoNHZcxOzMuCU4R2QAI\"}"